<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Process Cancelled</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif; background: #f1f5f9; margin: 0; padding: 40px 20px; }
        .container { max-width: 520px; margin: 0 auto; background: #fff; border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); overflow: hidden; }
        .header { background: #0f172a; padding: 32px; text-align: center; }
        .header h1 { color: #fff; margin: 0; font-size: 22px; font-weight: 600; }
        .body { padding: 32px; }
        .body p { color: #334155; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 16px; }
        .process-box { background: #fef2f2; border: 1px solid #fecaca; border-radius: 8px; padding: 16px; margin: 20px 0; }
        .process-box p { margin: 0; color: #991b1b; font-weight: 500; }
        .footer { padding: 20px 32px; border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0; }
        .footer p { color: #94a3b8; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.5; margin: 0; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Procivo</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="body">
            <p>Hello,</p>
            <p>The following process has been cancelled:</p>
            <div class="process-box">
                <p>{{ processName }}</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>You received this email because you are a member of a Procivo organization. To manage your notification preferences, visit your account settings.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
